---
import ImageSlideshow from './ImageSlideshow.astro';
---

<div class="space-y-6">
  <ImageSlideshow />
  
  <div class="prose prose-purple max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">About Me</h2>
    <div class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>
        As a multifaceted creator, I blend philosophical insights with comedic elements to make
        complex ideas accessible and entertaining. With a background in photography and book
        publishing, I bring a unique perspective to content creation.
      </p>
      <p>
        My journey began in traditional publishing, where I helped authors bring their ideas to
        life. Now, I'm expanding my horizons into web development, combining my creative skills
        with technical expertise to build engaging digital experiences.
      </p>
      <p>
        Through my content, I aim to bridge the gap between deep philosophical concepts and
        everyday life, making wisdom more accessible through humor and relatable examples.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9 mt-8">
    <iframe
      class="w-full h-[400px] rounded-xl"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XjG6_ej0j-o"
      title="YouTube video player"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen
    ></iframe>
  </div>
</div>
